(17, 0, '3. On Mercator\'s maps, the far northern and southern polar regions are....................', 'a. greatly exaggerated in area', 'b. exaggerating greatly in area.', 'c. greatly exaggerate in area.', 'd. great exaggeration in area.', 'A'),
