(23, 0, '9. ..................., the nation\'s capital remained in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.', 'a. While designing Washington, D.C.', 'b. Washington, D.C., was designed', 'c. While Washington, D.C., was being designed', 'd. Washington, D.C., designed', 'C'),
